node.text:
🥩🍰Dont you miss eating out? Can’t wait for all these to be over to be able to dine at my favourite restaurants again💗🥩🍰 ⁣
⁣
Looking for something to takeaway for meals, you can check out @oliviarestaurant_sg , I recall our tummies leaving happily after a great tapas meal + dessert! Their burnt cheesecake and croquette are yums!⁣
⁣
You can check out their takeaway menu (Swipe left) or head over to their ig for more details ❤️ Stay Safe everyone!⁣
⁣
